From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alexander Sack <asac@pantacor.com>
Date: Thu, 27 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] soc: arm: nxp: add mimx8mn6_m7 i.MX8M Nano M7 SOC

Add proper SOC definition for the i.MX8M Nano Cortex-M7 core.

Key differences from mimx8ml8_m7 (i.MX8M Plus M7):
- M7 clock: 600 MHz via SysPLL3 (Plus uses 800 MHz / SysPLL1)
- DDR code region: 0x7E000000 (Plus uses 0x80000000)
- Resource table at 0x400FF000 (matches Linux DTB rsc-table node)
- NUM_IRQS: 128 (Plus has 159)
- Part number: MIMX8MN6DVTJZ

Signed-off-by: Alexander Sack <asac@pantacor.com>
---
